{"data":[{"date":"16:19 09/07","title":"Pickford tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u201cb\u01a1\u201d Courtois v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/pickford-phat-bieu-ve-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pickford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford b\u1ecb Courtois ch\u00ea bai</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, \u0110T Anh th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. V\u1edbi pha solo \u0111i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Adnan Januzaj, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng G.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Januzaj ghi b\u00e0n, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 cho r\u1eb1ng anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y thay v\u00ec ch\u1ecdn sai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pickford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pickford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Pickford-phat-bieu-ve-Courtois-va-nhung-chi-trich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pickford t\u1eebng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p b\u00ean ph\u00eda Anh g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, Pickford \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Sunderland.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Pickford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng. \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh\u201d, Pickford n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u00ea b\u00ecnh n\u00e0o \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Pickford\" title=\"thu mon Pickford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/pickford-phat-bieu-ve-courtois.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pickford ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf t\u1ef1 tin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, nh\u01b0ng 2017/18 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf Premier League. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh qu\u00e1 thua k\u00e9m so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf (\u00e1m ch\u1ec9 Courtois). T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5p v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ee1 ng\u1ee1. D\u00f9 Premier League hay League One c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Pickford \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 pha c\u1ee9u thua ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Anh. \u0110i t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Croatia, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\">HLV Croatia \u0111\u1ec1 cao Sterling tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/davor-suke-noi-ve-dt-anh-465-190752.html\">Davor Suker: \u0110T Anh may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/truoc-dai-chien-nguoi-croatia-lay-messi-ra-doa-tuyen-anh-421-190735.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u1ea5y Messi ra d\u1ecda tuy\u1ec3n Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kane-muon-tam-su-la-doi-bong-cuoi-cung-tai-nuoc-nga-421-190734.html\">Kane mu\u1ed1n Tam S\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966-421-190733.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch 1966</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1075","checkdouble":"190781"},{"date":"16:31 09/07","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng Ligue 1 bay t\u1edbi London k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/21/jeanmichael-bay-toi-london-ky-hop-dong-voi-dai-gia-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jean-Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo France Football c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jean-Michael Seri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Jean-Michael Seri l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nice. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi\u1ebfn anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jean-Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jean-Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/26/Jean-Michael-Seri-ky-hop-dong-voi-Chelsea-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jean Michael Seri c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf NHA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-arsenal-va-chelsea-dang-dam-phan-voi-napoli-172-188308.html\" target=\"_blank\">Napoli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Jean-Michael Seri</span>, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Nice.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Napoli ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Michael Seri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jean-Michael Seri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo France Football c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng\u00a0v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFrance Football kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Nice \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea b\u1ecf ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Michael Seri</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Michael Seri, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal, Chelsea, Fulham v\u00e0 West Ham. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jean-Michael Seri la cau thu sang gia nhat cua Nice mua truoc\" title=\"Jean-Michael Seri l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nice m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/21/jeanmichael-bay-toi-london-ky-hop-dong-voi-dai-gia-premier-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jean-Michael Seri\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1eafp thay th\u1ebf Conte \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Michael Seri, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 v\u1edbi Nice ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Michael Seri t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, anh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Michael Seri s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1074","checkdouble":"190782"},{"date":"16:43 09/07","title":"Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Daniel Sturridge","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/26/klopp-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-daniel-sturridge.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e3y xem l\u1ea1i Raheem Sterling x\u1eed l\u00fd ra sao \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 khi c\u00e1i t\u1ed1t b\u1ecb che m\u1edd b\u1edfi c\u00e1i d\u1edf, khi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, di chuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng b\u1ed7ng ch\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed5 s\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 v\u00ec c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n, khi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 trong t\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y n\u1eeda n\u0103m.</span></p>\r\n<table cellpacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"44px\"><img src=\"/content/images/s1.png\" alt=\"comment left\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: justify;\"><em>Raheem \u0111\u1ee7 hi\u1ec3u nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1ng n\u1ed5i trong nh\u1eefng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1ebfu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ghi b\u00e0n. Raheem c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn m\u00e0 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch th\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1o t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u01a1n b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 \u0111\u00f3.</em></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"44px\"><img src=\"/content/images/s2.png\" alt=\"comment right\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">N\u1ebfu HLV c\u1ee7a Mancheter City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5 ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1ebft n\u00ean l\u00e0 pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">C\u00e1i l\u1eebng kh\u1eebng c\u1ee7a Sterling khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i s\u1ef1 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c sau \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-o-tran-colombia-vs-anh-nguoi-thu-linh-phot-tinh-ang-le-421-190324.html\" target=\"_blank\">g\u00e3 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \"ph\u1edbt t\u1ec9nh \u0102ng-l\u00ea\" Harry Kane</span> c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t c\u00e1u ra m\u1eb7t khi b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n anh khi \u0111ang theo \u0111\u00e0 b\u0103ng l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea1ch r\u00f2i ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, v\u1edbi Sterling ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00f4 l\u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00f4 l\u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Sterling-o-doi-tuyen-Anh-dang-bi-hieu-lam-va-chi-trich-vo-ly-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 n\u00e9n nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3. C\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Sterling ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Kane, n\u00ean anh s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb soi m\u00f3i, x\u00e9t n\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u1eaft khe v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c \u0111oan th\u00e1i qu\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00f3 sau c\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00e1m n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup, v\u1edbi Sterling ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y hay ho n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi-421-190658.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup: L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-vs-thuy-dien-dele-alli-421-190660.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup: Ng\u00e0y Dele Alli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Kh\u00f4ng ai th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 anh x\u00e9t tr\u00ean kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a anh trong su\u1ed1t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng trong khi th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Sterling kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng n\u00e0o h\u1ebft, h\u00e3y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn vai tr\u00f2 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng quan tr\u1ecdng t\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a anh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Tam S\u01b0.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">K\u1ec3 ra m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Sterling d\u00f9 g\u00ec c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y v\u1edbi 23 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Man City trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1i \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t \u1edf ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a anh, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean tho\u00e1t ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o s\u00e1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Sterling Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Sterling-Nhan-vat-dang-bi-hieu-lam-nhat-xu-suong-mu-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong c\u1ea3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, Sterling c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn hy sinh, l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. Anh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng di chuy\u1ec3n, h\u1ebft d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u00f9i s\u00e2u th\u1eadm ch\u00ed xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi ph\u00eda sau khu trung tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 r\u00ea d\u1eaft kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang c\u00e1ch di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng r\u1ed9ng kh\u1eafp m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sterling kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh khi ph\u1ea3i c\u1eaft c\u1eed c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y theo \u0111eo b\u00e1m k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00ean tr\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Li\u1ec7u Sterling c\u00f3 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o? R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng. Li\u1ec7u Sterling \u0111\u00e3 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc so v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh so v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng trong hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Man City c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf Liverpool? Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Sterling Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00f4 l\u00fd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u00edt c\u00f3 \u00fd n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 an \u1ee7i g\u00ec Sterling khi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Croatia kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 x\u00e3 giao</span> khi chia s\u1ebb r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd vui m\u1eebng ra sao khi ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu Sterling kh\u00f4ng ch\u00f4n ch\u00e2n ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f9ng Balkan s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 lo l\u1eafng nh\u01b0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb x\u1edbi tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Sterling s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u00ednh kh\u00ed thi\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh? Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 anh.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#333333\">T\u1ea1i sao Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00f4 l\u00fd?<br>\r\n</span></strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/9/Raz.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#333333\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1073","checkdouble":"190783"},{"date":"16:48 09/07","title":"N\u00d3NG: Hai ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/nong-hai-ngoi-sao-den-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1eady t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o David Ornstein c\u1ee7a t\u1edd BBC th\u00ec CLB Arsenal v\u1eeba \u0111\u00f3n 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 9/7.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;V\u00e0 sau c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mang t\u00ean Stephan Lichtsteiner, Bernd Leno v\u00e0 Sokratis Papastathopoulos, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ti\u1ebfp theo.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Torreira va Matteo Guendouzi sap cap ben Arsenal\" title=\"Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/lucas-torreira-972041-15288579744461655481829.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Lucas Torreira (tr\u00e1i) v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi (ph\u1ea3i) s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 hai g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u1eddi gian qua v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u CLB bao g\u1ed3m: ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Uruguay, Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U20 Ph\u00e1p, Matteo Guendouzi.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Torreira n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB Sampdoria t\u1ea1i Seria A, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Uruguay tham d\u1ef1 VCK World Cup 2018. Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Unai Emery.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Guendouzi \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 19 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p s\u1edf h\u1eefu. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb tay c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Tottenham v\u00e0 M.U, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi cho CLB Lorient s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo BBC, c\u1ea3 hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i London \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Arsenal. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o x\u1ea3y ra, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng The Gunners s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 hai h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1072","checkdouble":"190784"},{"date":"16:46 09/07","title":"Xavi ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Xavi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft anh ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t k\u1ebf th\u1eeba Julen Lopetegui.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. B\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Julen Lopetegui k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng qua c\u1ea5p tr\u00ean, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (RFEF) \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ea1nh tay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau khi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o Lopetegui s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Real h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Luis Rubiales \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp kh\u1ea9n. Sau khi tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 40 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i sa th\u1ea3i c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Porto.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xavi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xavi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-HLV-Tay-Ban-Nha-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nFernando Hierro l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean ch\u00e8o l\u00e1i \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c La Roja \u0111i t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Nga sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Xavi kh\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec Enrique \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau World Cup 2018, Hierro t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5t nh\u1eafc l\u00ean l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. RFEF d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd m\u1eddi Luis Enrique ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u00f2n tr\u1ed1ng sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp c\u1ea5p cao s\u00e1ng nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xavi va Messi\" title=\"Xavi va Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/xavi-phat-bieu-ve-ghe-hlv-tay-ban-nha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Xavi kh\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec b\u1ecb \u0110T\u00a0TBN ng\u00f3 l\u01a1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXavi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 gh\u1ebf HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Anh kh\u00f4ng bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 b\u1edfi tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng\u201d, Xavi n\u00f3i v\u1edbi AS. \u201cTh\u1ee9 2, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 3, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi gh\u1ebf HLV \u0110TQG. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi th\u00eam, ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-fernando-hierro-roi-ghe-hlv-truong-cua-tbn-421-190705.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Fernando Hierro r\u1eddi gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-466-190435.html\">World Cup 2018: 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bi-co-the-dan-dat-tay-ban-nha-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190427.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ky-world-cup-cua-tay-ban-nha-khong-te-nhu-nguoi-ta-nghi-421-190397.html\">K\u1ef3 World Cup c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ngh\u0129</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1071","checkdouble":"190785"},{"date":"16:43 09/07","title":"Sterling: Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/sterling-nhan-vat-dang-bi-hieu-lam-nhat-xu-suong-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e3y xem l\u1ea1i Raheem Sterling x\u1eed l\u00fd ra sao \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 khi c\u00e1i t\u1ed1t b\u1ecb che m\u1edd b\u1edfi c\u00e1i d\u1edf, khi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, di chuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng b\u1ed7ng ch\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed5 s\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 v\u00ec c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n, khi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 trong t\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y n\u1eeda n\u0103m.</span></p>\r\n<table cellpacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"44px\"><img src=\"/content/images/s1.png\" alt=\"comment left\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 10px; text-align: justify;\"><em>Raheem \u0111\u1ee7 hi\u1ec3u nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1ng n\u1ed5i trong nh\u1eefng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1ebfu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ghi b\u00e0n. Raheem c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn m\u00e0 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch th\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1o t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u01a1n b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 \u0111\u00f3.</em></td>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" width=\"44px\"><img src=\"/content/images/s2.png\" alt=\"comment right\" width=\"44px\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">N\u1ebfu HLV c\u1ee7a Mancheter City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5 ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1ebft n\u00ean l\u00e0 pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">C\u00e1i l\u1eebng kh\u1eebng c\u1ee7a Sterling khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i s\u1ef1 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c sau \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-o-tran-colombia-vs-anh-nguoi-thu-linh-phot-tinh-ang-le-421-190324.html\" target=\"_blank\">g\u00e3 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \"ph\u1edbt t\u1ec9nh \u0102ng-l\u00ea\" Harry Kane</span> c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t c\u00e1u ra m\u1eb7t khi b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n anh khi \u0111ang theo \u0111\u00e0 b\u0103ng l\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea1ch r\u00f2i ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, v\u1edbi Sterling ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00f4 l\u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00f4 l\u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Sterling-o-doi-tuyen-Anh-dang-bi-hieu-lam-va-chi-trich-vo-ly-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 n\u00e9n nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3. C\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Sterling ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Kane, n\u00ean anh s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb soi m\u00f3i, x\u00e9t n\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u1eaft khe v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c \u0111oan th\u00e1i qu\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00f3 sau c\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00e1m n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup, v\u1edbi Sterling ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y hay ho n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi-421-190658.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup: L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-vs-thuy-dien-dele-alli-421-190660.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup: Ng\u00e0y Dele Alli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Kh\u00f4ng ai th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 anh x\u00e9t tr\u00ean kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a anh trong su\u1ed1t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng trong khi th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Sterling kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng n\u00e0o h\u1ebft, h\u00e3y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn vai tr\u00f2 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng quan tr\u1ecdng t\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a anh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Tam S\u01b0.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">K\u1ec3 ra m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Sterling d\u00f9 g\u00ec c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y v\u1edbi 23 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Man City trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1i \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t \u1edf ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a anh, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean tho\u00e1t ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o s\u00e1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Sterling Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Sterling-Nhan-vat-dang-bi-hieu-lam-nhat-xu-suong-mu-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong c\u1ea3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, Sterling c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn hy sinh, l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. Anh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng di chuy\u1ec3n, h\u1ebft d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u00f9i s\u00e2u th\u1eadm ch\u00ed xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi ph\u00eda sau khu trung tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 r\u00ea d\u1eaft kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang c\u00e1ch di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng r\u1ed9ng kh\u1eafp m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Sterling kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh khi ph\u1ea3i c\u1eaft c\u1eed c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y theo \u0111eo b\u00e1m k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00ean tr\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Li\u1ec7u Sterling c\u00f3 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o? R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng. Li\u1ec7u Sterling \u0111\u00e3 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc so v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh so v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng trong hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Man City c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf Liverpool? Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Sterling Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00f4 l\u00fd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u00edt c\u00f3 \u00fd n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 an \u1ee7i g\u00ec Sterling khi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-de-cao-sterling-truoc-tran-ban-ket-gap-dt-anh-421-190780.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Croatia kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 x\u00e3 giao</span> khi chia s\u1ebb r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd vui m\u1eebng ra sao khi ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu Sterling kh\u00f4ng ch\u00f4n ch\u00e2n ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f9ng Balkan s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 lo l\u1eafng nh\u01b0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb x\u1edbi tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Sterling s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u00ednh kh\u00ed thi\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh? Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 anh.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#333333\">T\u1ea1i sao Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00f4 l\u00fd?<br>\r\n</span></strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/9/Raz.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#333333\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1070","checkdouble":"190786"},{"date":"17:49 09/07","title":"B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 sao Man City \u1edf World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/bo-doi-huyen-thoai-mu-bao-ve-sao-man-city-o-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gary Neville v\u00e0 David Beckham \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e0n em Raheem Sterling v\u1ed1n \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 qua, v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Croatia \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n h\u1ecd. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i hi\u1ebfm hoi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n th\u1eddi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Raheem Sterling.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/bo-doi-huyen-thoai-mu-bao-ve-sao-man-city-o-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111ang d\u1ea7n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng cho t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, Sterling v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n im h\u01a1i l\u1eb7ng ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. K\u1ec3 ra th\u00ec c\u01a1n h\u1ea1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Man City c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 hai t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 Sterling ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. Tuy nhi\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/sterling-nhan-vat-dang-bi-hieu-lam-nhat-xu-suong-mu-421-190786.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111ang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m</span> v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1ch quan v\u1ec1 vai tr\u00f2 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ebf n\u00ean m\u1ed9t Gary Neville n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh, kh\u1eaft khe c\u0169ng ra s\u1ee9c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Sterling: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 v\u00e0i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng. Sterling v\u00e3n \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 chim m\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 David Beckham c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169: \u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ecdc nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh cho Sterling nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 \u0111\u00fang sai ra sao, ch\u00fang v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup c\u01a1 m\u00e0, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n vinh. Ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ee9ng sau \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/9/Raz.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1069","checkdouble":"190787"},{"date":"17:37 09/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Singapore 19h00 ng\u00e0y 9/7 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-singapore-ngay-hom-nay-97.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Real Madrid vs Betis: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid vs Betis v\u00f2ng 27 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG T\u00e2y Ban Nha TBN La Liga 2016/17 l\u00fac 02h45 ng\u00e0y 13/3.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Singapore</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\n- U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 c\u00f3 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a U19 Indonesia, U19 Myanmar, U19 Philippines v\u00e0 U19 Brunei.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 v\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3o, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5 m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 so v\u1edbi U19 Indonesia v\u00e0 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. Sau 4 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi c\u00f3 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u00edt h\u01a1n 2 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 3 v\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eadm U19 Singapore, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi hy v\u1ecdng U19 Indonesia d\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i U19 Th\u00e1i Lan.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Singapore 19h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 97 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Singapore 19h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 97 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-01-u19-indonesia-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong kh\u00e2u d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ch\u00ednh HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi U19 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 U19 Indonesia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 U19 Singapore. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-0. 1 n\u0103m sau, d\u00f9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u1edbi Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh\u2026, nh\u01b0ng U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 0-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1068","checkdouble":"190790"},{"date":"17:37 09/07","title":"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/4-diem-nhan-sau-vong-tu-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u01b0\u1edbc Nga \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2>Khi b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111ang nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi \u0110T Anh nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Trong 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft (\u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c). V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Harry Kane, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 8/11. Tam S\u01b0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n l\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft l\u00e0m l\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong h\u01a1n 20 n\u0103m qua, sau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Uruguay, b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Antoine Griezmann t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng, Raphael Varane b\u0103ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u, v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Croatia c\u0169ng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga l\u00ean 2-1 t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c. \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9, khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf bu\u1ed9c Fernandinho ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Nhung-diem-nhan-vong-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1 cao nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>C\u1ee9 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 thua<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, chuy\u1ec7n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eddi v\u1ec1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh. Theo \u0111\u00f3, s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 vs Brazil &ndash; khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng 2 b\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng sang ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n b\u00ean kia \u0111\u1ec3 bu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa. \u1ede ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, h\u1ecd c\u1eaft c\u1eed 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u00e8m m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Neymar, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i \u0103n 2 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng (c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a De Bruyne).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng v\u1eady, khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt r\u1ea5t linh ho\u1ea1t b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 Uruguay thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Cavani. Nh\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nam M\u1ef9 no \u0111\u00f2n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Deschamps m\u1edbi s\u0103n m\u1ed3i b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 ch\u0103ng, ch\u1ec9 \u0110T Anh l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ki\u1ebfm ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c. V\u00e0 khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 nh\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Con ac mong cua Neymar\" title=\"C\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/091617-neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Brazil th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00ec B\u1ec9 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ec1 cao s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng, vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. 2 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0ng t\u00fac c\u1ea7u, Leo Messi v\u00e0 Cris Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1ch vali v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Neymar c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u1ed3ng g\u00e1nh Brazil l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kylian Mbappe, sao tr\u1ebb \u0111ang l\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Uruguay. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;ng\u1ee9a m\u1eaft&rdquo;, v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0103n v\u1ea1 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Neymar. B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Uruguay t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i to\u00e0n t\u1eadp khi Luis Suarez im ti\u1ebfng, c\u00f2n Edinson Cavani ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c HLV hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng d\u00f9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 m\u1edbi gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe an va tho thien trong tran thang DT Uruguay\" title=\"Mbappe \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110T Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/noi-guong-neymar-mbappe-suyt-nua-bi-tan-vi-hoc-doi-thoi-an-va.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe h\u1ecdc l\u00e0m di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean thay v\u00ec t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Brazil. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p. Jordan Pickford trong gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u, gi\u00fap Tam S\u01b0 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau 3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois c\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ch\u1eb3ng k\u00e9m, v\u1edbi pha c\u1ee9u thua si\u00eau t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 n\u00e0y, Brazil s\u1ebd g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2, v\u00e0 n\u1eafm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tinh th\u1ea7n. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean, l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat Nacer Chadli v\u00e0 Romelu Lukaku ra ngh\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7/ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois\" title=\"Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a h\u1ebft, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Subasic c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p n\u1eeda c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c cho chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, khi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong 2 lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang. Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 sau \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1m ngh\u1ec9, ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam mai (01h00 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 4, ng\u00e0y 11/7).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam video l\u00fd do Sterling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/9/Raz.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhung-vong-ban-ket-noi-chien-au-chau-421-190775.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhung-vong-ban-ket-noi-chien-au-chau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-27-nhung-vong-ban-ket-noi-chien-au-chau-421-190775.html\">S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 27: Nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft &ldquo;n\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn&rdquo; \u00c2u ch\u00e2u</span><br>\r\nWorld Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9c 4 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00e0 B\u1ec9, Ph\u00e1p, Anh v\u00e0 Croatia. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 4 VCK x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1....</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-sau-3-thap-ky-fan-cuong-nhay-tu-xe-bus-xuong-an-mung-421-190684.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau 3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7, fan cu\u1ed3ng&hellip; nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus xu\u1ed1ng \u0103n m\u1eebng</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ngu d\u1ed1t c\u0169ng v\u1eady. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u1ea3y t\u1eeb xe bus 2 t\u1ea7ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tam...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat-465-190664.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat-465-190664.html\">B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Man Utd \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh m\u00e0 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 \u0111ang th\u1eafng l\u1edbn khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n 50 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1067","checkdouble":"190791"},{"date":"17:53 09/07","title":"Alex Sandro \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/9/alex-sandro-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-hau-ve-trai-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Sandro \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. C\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcos Alonso (Chelsea)</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Marcos Alonso l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 3-5-2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Conte v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 cho th\u1ea5y anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Sandro N\u00ean hay kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Sandro N\u00ean hay kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/MU-muon-mua-Alex-Sandro-Nen-hay-khong-nen-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcos Alonso</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMarcos Alonso l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t Premier League 2017/18, anh c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 7 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m rung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Alex Sandro c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 8 trong danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, Sandro l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n. 75% s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Alonso l\u00e0 70%. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Sandro c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Alonso (44 so v\u1edbi 16).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, Sandro t\u1ea1o ra 27 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 4 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u1edbi Alonso, anh t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 34 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i, Alonso (1m88) kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Sandro (1m80). C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u00f3 61 l\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 38.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Andrew Robertson (Liverpool)</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng Andrew Robertson \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng vi\u1ec7c Alberto Moreno d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp b\u1eb1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andrew Robertson\" title=\"Andrew Robertson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/robertson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andrew Robertson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSo v\u1edbi Alex Sandro, Andrew Robertson ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n (1 so v\u1edbi 4), nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i anh l\u1ea1i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o h\u01a1n (5 so v\u1edbi 4).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra 21 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng 5 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n ho\u00e1n th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Sandro t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 27 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&nbsp;\u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Robertson l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u1ee9 2 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, Sandro ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat so v\u1edbi Robertson (27 so v\u1edbi 26), nh\u01b0ng n\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n g\u1ea7n 200 ph\u00fat (2115 ph\u00fat so v\u1edbi 1943 ph\u00fat).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ben Davies (Tottenham)</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Ben Davies ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Danny Rose m\u1edbi l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Tottenham. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mauricio Pochettino tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ben Davies\" title=\"Ben Davies\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/ben-davies.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ben Davies</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Ben Davies kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Alex Sandro (2 so v\u1edbi 4), nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o anh l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i (6 so v\u1edbi 4). Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 47 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi 27 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Ben Davies ch\u1ec9 22 l\u1ea7n m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng, so v\u1edbi 44 c\u1ee7a Sandro l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-o-vi-tri-hau-ve-trai-172-182680.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Sandro</span>, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ryan Bertrand (Southampton)</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ryan Bertrand l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o sau 35 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Premier League 2017/18, khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh con s\u1ed1 4 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Sandro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ryan Bentrand\" title=\"Ryan Bentrand\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/bentrand.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ryan Bentrand</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, c\u1ea3 Ryan Bertrand v\u00e0 Sandro \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, song ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Southampton t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n (36 so v\u1edbi 27).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 Bertrand v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Sandro. C\u1ef1u sao Chelsea c\u00f3 34 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 43 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 27 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 23 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nacho Monreal (Arsenal)</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nacho Monreal \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Monreal\" title=\"Monreal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/16/hlv-wenger-monreal-khong-con-la-mot-hau-ve-trai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nacho Monreal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ghi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 21 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Sandro (4 b\u00e0n sau 17 l\u1ea7n k\u1ebft th\u00fac). V\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, Monreal ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra 14 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, kh\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n so v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus (27 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, 4&nbsp;ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 27 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, song v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n Monreal v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1edbi 49 so v\u1edbi 23.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n*Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1066","checkdouble":"190792"},{"date":"09:02 09/07","title":"Sao s\u00e1ng World Cup x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/torreira-sap-toi-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lucas Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. Ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Torreira t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u00e0 World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u0103m 2013, Lucas Torreira r\u1eddi qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Uruguay \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Italia \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Pescara. Ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Serie B, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Sampdoria v\u00e0 h\u1ecd chi 1,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 anh. Sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 Torreira ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i cho Pescara d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u00f9a 2015/16, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng tri\u1ec7u h\u1ed3i anh v\u1ec1 v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 2 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua, Torreira \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i 35 tr\u1eadn tr\u1edf l\u00ean t\u1ea1i Serie A cho Sampdoria. \u1ede m\u00f9a 2017/18, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ph\u00e1t ti\u1ebft m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng (ch\u1ec9 cao 1m68) song Torreira c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Torreira-sap-toi-Arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Torreira ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i Sampdoria</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Torreira n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nhanh nh\u01b0 c\u1eaft. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Uruguay c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t hay s\u00fat xa\u2026 T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Serie A hay m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau m\u00f9a 2017/18, Arsenal v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 Torreira \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1o li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Sampdoria \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua anh. Sau c\u00f9ng, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 26,4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Torreira\" title=\"tien ve Torreira\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/torreira-sap-toi-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, sau khi Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0111i k\u00e8m Torreira s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. Anh c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f9ng ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Uruguay c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, Torreira n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Telenoche. \u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed n\u00f3.\u201d <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi Arsenal, Torreira s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng Stephan Lichtsteiner, Bernd Leno v\u00e0 Sokratis Papastathopoulos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV m\u1edbi Unai Emery thay Arsene Wenger.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-arsenal-van-chua-the-cong-bo-thuong-vu-torreira-172-190606.html\">V\u00ec sao Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Torreira?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-arsenal-chi-27-trieu-bang-mua-cristian-pavon-172-190516.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal chi 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Cristian Pavon</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-vu-sao-khung-argentina-421-190433.html\">Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-barca-172-190353.html\">Arsenal b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1065","checkdouble":"190746"},{"date":"10:02 09/07","title":"Arsenal chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/arsenal-chuan-bi-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-than-dong-guendouzi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0a tin, Arsenal \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Matteo Guendouzi.</h2><h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Matteo Guendouzi\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin \u0111\u1ed3n Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Guendouzi trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin \u0111\u1ed3n Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Guendouzi trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/arsenal-chuan-bi-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-than-dong-guendouzi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Guendouzi, th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/arsenal-4.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal</span> \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Lorient \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Matteo Guendouzi h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i. Anh l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb PSG nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Lorient n\u0103m 2014.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd RMC Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t v\u00e0 Guendouzi s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi London trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates. Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y khi Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB Lorient c\u1ee7a Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng kh\u1ecfi Ligue 1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tranh su\u1ea5t th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Guendouzi c\u00f3 21 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u01a1i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u00fd do Guendouzi r\u1eddi Lorient \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1 quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Lorient. Anh b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Do v\u1eady, ra \u0111i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Guendouzi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1ea1i Ph\u1ea7n Lan s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 khi Torreira c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi London sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay \u1edf World Cup 2018. Theo nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Torreira, anh s\u1ebd ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m London Colney trong h\u00f4m nay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/torreira-sap-toi-arsenal-kiem-tra-y-te-172-190746.html\">Sao s\u00e1ng World Cup x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-arsenal-van-chua-the-cong-bo-thuong-vu-torreira-172-190606.html\">V\u00ec sao Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Torreira?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1064","checkdouble":"190748"},{"date":"09:27 09/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed5i gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng U19 \u0110N\u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/doi-gio-thi-dau-u19-viet-nam-con-co-hoi-vuot-qua-vong-bang-u19-dna.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Elneny t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 khi Arsenal b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd.</h2><h2>Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo. Anh kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn derby London v\u1edbi West Ham h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Elneny \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc Phi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Pharaoh c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m do \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 c\u00f9ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 c\u00f9ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/elneny-hao-huc-truoc-mua-giai-201819-cung-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Elneny h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay l\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Emirates, Elneny \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. HLV Unai Emery s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y sau khi HLV Wenger ra \u0111i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Elneny v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau khi tham d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p Boreham Wood v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14/7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u0103ng n\u1ed5. HLV Unai Emery b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ecdng y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno, trung\u00a0 v\u1ec7 Sokratis, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Lichtsteiner l\u00e0 3 t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Lucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u0169ng m\u1edbi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn London ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chuan-bi-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-than-dong-guendouzi-172-190748.html\">Arsenal chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-arsenal-van-chua-the-cong-bo-thuong-vu-torreira-172-190606.html\">V\u00ec sao Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Torreira?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1063","checkdouble":"190749"},{"date":"09:46 09/07","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/cong-phuong-len-tieng-sau-tinh-huong-mat-kiem-che-voi-thu-mon-tuan-manh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh b\u00ean ph\u00eda Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee9a thay \u0111\u1ed5i sau pha&nbsp;n\u1ed5i n\u00f3ng v\u1edbi Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa HAGL vs Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Pleiku \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 4-2, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0nh vi n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn l\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi qua ti\u1ebfng l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, bu\u1ed9c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"cong phuong\" title=\"c\u00f4ng ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/cong-phuong-len-tieng-sau-tinh-huong-mat-kiem-che-voi-thu-mon-tuan-manh.png\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ef1c t\u1ee9c v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00e2u gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. \u1ea2nh: Sport5.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb HLV Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 \u00fd g\u00e2y h\u1ea5n sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Th\u00f4ng qua trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Anh n\u00f3i: &quot;H\u00f4m nay th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y kh\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0ng mong l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng tin v\u00e0 hi v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00ecnh bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng m\u00ecnh lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. H\u00f4m nay, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e3y hi\u1ec3u cho m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea7n t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 &ldquo;bu\u1ed3n&rdquo; c\u00f2n bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec c\u00e1i g\u00ec ch\u1eafc m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u00f9ng nhau c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HAGL. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai. Tuy nhi\u00ean Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League sau vong 18\" title=\"BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/BXH-V-League-sau-vong-18.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League sau v\u00f2ng 18</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-kich-tinh-hagl-24-khanh-hoa-168-190725.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh HAGL 2-4 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm song CLB HAGL cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. V\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-bi-che-truong-doan-hagl-noi-gi-168-190720.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-tuan-manh-dang-dan-chi-trich-cong-phuong-choi-xau-168-190719.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p HAGL.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-ly-giai-ve-hanh-dong-thieu-fairplay-cua-cong-phuong-168-190714.html\">HLV HAGL l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu fair-play c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh cho r\u1eb1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1062","checkdouble":"190750"},{"date":"11:07 09/07","title":"Davor Suker: \"\u0110T Anh may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf World Cup 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/davor-suke-noi-ve-dt-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Croatia, Davor Suker n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u1edbi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3m, cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate c\u00f2n \u1edf l\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 nh\u1edd may m\u1eafn.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Davor Suker n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>R\u01a1i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3, \u0110T Anh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng khi &quot;ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng&quot; thua B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i. Nh\u1edd v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng, Tam S\u01b0 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh &quot;d\u1ec5 th\u1edf&quot; h\u01a1n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Colombia v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Davor Suker n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Davor Suker n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Davor-Suker-noi-ve-DT-Anh-Ho-da-may-man-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Davor Suker cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTam S\u01b0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m. T\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Croatia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Davor Suker. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 20 n\u0103m, Croatia m\u1edbi t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, sau th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Davor Suker t\u1ea1i World Cup 1998.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Davor Suker, \u0110T Anh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf World Cup 2018: &quot;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Anh vs Colombia t\u1ea1i Moscow, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t may m\u1eafn. Colombia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hai c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean trong lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho c\u1ea3 hai?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0110T Anh may m\u1eafn nh\u01b0ng Davor Suker cho r\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 may r\u1ee7i: &quot;V\u00ec sao c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 may m\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3? B\u1edfi l\u1ebd c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i th\u00edch. \u0110T Anh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, 11 \u0111\u1ea5u 11, 11 chi\u1ebfn binh&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ti\u1ec1n, xe Ferrari hay \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00fd g\u00ec \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea3, ch\u1ec9 11 \u0111\u1ea5u 11 \u1edf World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i th\u00edch. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga r\u1ed3i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Croatia v\u00e0 Anh l\u00e0 50 - 50&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Croatia vs Anh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-se-het-do-o-ban-ket-vi-chuyen-nay-421-190757.html\">Anh s\u1ebd h\u1ebft &ldquo;\u0111\u1ecf&rdquo; \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kane-muon-tam-su-la-doi-bong-cuoi-cung-tai-nuoc-nga-421-190734.html\">Kane mu\u1ed1n Tam S\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-anh-dang-san-sang-lap-lai-chien-tich-1966-421-190733.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch 1966</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/paul-scholes-pep-co-anh-huong-den-thanh-cong-cua-dt-anh-421-190713.html\">Paul Scholes: Pep c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-tuyen-anh-duoc-khen-het-loi-sau-khi-giup-doi-nha-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-421-190696.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen h\u1ebft l\u1eddi sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-pickford-noi-gi-sau-khi-dt-anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-28-nam-421-190692.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pickford n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi \u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1061","checkdouble":"190752"}]}